trans-unit.source: Represents a member of a type using a literal code fragment.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en medlem av en typ med ett litteralt kodfragment.

trans-unit.source: CodeSnippetTypeMember can represent a member of a type using a literal code fragment that is included directly in the source without modification.
trans-unit.target: CodeSnippetTypeMember kan representera en medlem av en typ med ett litteralt kodfragment direkt i källan utan modifiering.

trans-unit.source: This code can be included in the type declaration.
trans-unit.target: Den här koden kan ingå i typdeklarationen.

trans-unit.source: A CodeSnippetTypeMember stores a section of code, exactly in its original format, as a string.
trans-unit.target: En CodeSnippetTypeMember lagras en del av kod, exakt i dess ursprungliga format, som en sträng.

trans-unit.source: The CodeDOM does not translate literal code fragments.
Literal code fragments are stored and output in their original format.
trans-unit.target: Literalen kodfragment lagras och utdata i deras ursprungliga format.

trans-unit.source: CodeDOM objects that contain literal code are provided so developers can encapsulate code that is already in the target language.
trans-unit.target: CodeDOM-objekt som innehåller literal kod tillhandahålls så att utvecklare kan kapsla kod som redan finns på språket som mål.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetTypeMember.Text%2A> property contains the literal code for the type member.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetTypeMember"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetTypeMember"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetTypeMember"></xref> class using the specified text.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.CodeDom.CodeSnippetTypeMember"> </xref> klassen med hjälp av den angivna texten.

trans-unit.source: The literal code fragment for the type member.
Gets or sets the literal code fragment for the type member.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger literal kodfragmentet för typen medlem.

trans-unit.source: The literal code fragment for the type member.
